      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard of excellence. This specimen represents the absolute pinnacle of its class, preserved in showroom condition with impeccable interior appointments and flawless mechanical integrity. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
